Searchlight Opportunities Fund, L.P.  Financing
Searchlight Opportunities Fund, L.P. just submitted form D announcing  Indefinite equity financing.  This is a new filing. Searchlight Opportunities Fund, L.P. was able to sell $325,000,000. The total private offering amount was Indefinite. The financing was made by 2 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $0. The financing document was filed on 2016-12-02. Searchlight Opportunities Fund, L.P. is based in  C/O SEARCHLIGHT CAPITAL PARTNERS, L.P. 745 FIFTH AVENUE, 27TH FLOOR NEW YORK 10151. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The form was signed by  N/A Searchlight Opportunities Fund GP, L.P..





